00011 inline string str_replace(std::string str, const std::string& oldStr, const std::string& newStr)
00012 {
00013   size_t pos = 0;
00014   while((pos = str.find(oldStr, pos)) != std::string::npos)
00015   {
00016      str.replace(pos, oldStr.length(), newStr);
00017      pos += newStr.length();
00018   }
00019   return str;
00020 }

00022 inline string prettyprint(const string& str) {
00023   string clean = str_replace(str, "\n", "\\n");
00024   clean = str_replace(clean, "  ", "\\t");
00025   clean = str_replace(clean, "\r", "\\r");
00026   return clean;
00027 }

00035 inline string pstate_source_position(AST_Node* node)
00036 {
00037   stringstream str;
00038   Position start(node->pstate());
00039   Position end(start + node->pstate().offset);
00040   str << (start.file == string::npos ? -1 : start.file)
00041     << "@[" << start.line << ":" << start.column << "]"
00042     << "-[" << end.line << ":" << end.column << "]";
00043   return str.str();
00044 }
